OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1779109902
OL,3,CSchool issued with government funding
OL,4,Cthreat after teen's murder
OL,6,FThe high school where teenager Harvey
OL,7,FWillgoose was murdered has been warned
OL,8,Fit could lose government funding
OL,9,Funless it improves safeguarding
OL,10,Fmeasures.
OL,12,FHarvey was 15 when he was stabbed with
OL,13,Fa hunting knife by fellow pupil, 15-
OL,14,Fyear-old Mohammed Umar Khan, at
OL,15,FSheffield's All Saints Catholic High
OL,16,FSchool in February last year.
OL,18,FAn independent review commissioned by
OL,19,Fthe school found it failed to take
OL,20,Faction to address Khan's behaviour
OL,21,Fdespite a history of violence.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/9
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,368,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1779109902
OL,3,CSchool issued with government funding
OL,4,Cthreat after teen's murder
OL,6,FNow the Department for Education has
OL,7,Fserved All Saints with a notice to
OL,8,Fimprove.
OL,10,FThe notice, published on Friday, said
OL,11,Fthe trust had "failed to comply with
OL,12,Fsafeguarding measures" and provided a
OL,13,Flist of recommendations, including
OL,14,Frevising its current child protection
OL,15,Fpolicies.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/9
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,368,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1779109902
OL,3,CSchool issued with government funding
OL,4,Cthreat after teen's murder
OL,6,FIt added: "In the event that the trust
OL,7,Ffails to meet the requirements of this
OL,8,Fnotice, to the satisfaction of the
OL,9,FSecretary of State, it will be
OL,10,Fconsidered to have failed to comply
OL,11,Fwith the terms of the Academy Trust
OL,12,FHandbook (ATH).
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/9
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,368,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1779109902
OL,3,CSchool issued with government funding
OL,4,Cthreat after teen's murder
OL,6,F"This will amount to a breach of the
OL,7,Fterms of the funding agreement and may
OL,8,Flead to termination (of the funding
OL,9,Fagreement). If continued non-
OL,10,Fcompliance with the ATH occurs, we may
OL,11,Falso refer the case to the Charity
OL,12,FCommission for further investigation,
OL,13,Fas deemed appropriate in the
OL,14,Fcircumstances."
OL,16,FKhan, 15, was jailed for life and told
OL,17,Fhe would serve a minimum of 16 years
OL,18,Fat Sheffield Crown Court last October,
OL,19,Fafter being found guilty of murder.
OL,26,@pD@UpmqD@Jpn
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/9
