PN,36705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1779109902
OL,3,CSchool issued with government funding
OL,4,Cthreat after teen's murder
OL,6,FA subsequent review - carried out by a
OL,7,Fformer headteacher and inspector of
OL,8,Fschools - found that school leaders
OL,9,F"could, and at times should, have
OL,10,Ftaken different action" and were
OL,11,Fguilty of "oversights, assumptions and
OL,12,Fmisjudgements".
OL,14,FIt identified weaknesses in
OL,15,Fleadership, gaps in policy, poor
OL,16,Fimplementation of government guidance
OL,17,Fand serious shortcomings in
OL,18,Frecordkeeping that meant
OL,19,Fweaponsrelated concerns and worrying
OL,20,Fbehaviours were not acted upon
OL,21,Feffectively.
OL,26,@qD@AOUsD@KOU
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/9
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,368,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1779109902
OL,3,CSchool issued with government funding
OL,4,Cthreat after teen's murder
OL,6,FAccording to Harvey's family the
OL,7,Freview documented 130 "red flag"
OL,8,Fincidents at Khan's previous school.
OL,10,FThe DfE's notice to improve said the
OL,11,Fschool needed to demonstrate it had
OL,12,Fstrengthened "safeguarding oversight,
OL,13,Fgovernance and assurance arrangements".
OL,15,FThe notice "is focused on systems and
OL,16,Fprocesses, rather than on individuals
OL,17,For specific events, and it does not
OL,18,Fseek to draw conclusions about, or
OL,19,Fattribute responsibility for, the
OL,20,Fcircumstances surrounding Harvey's
OL,21,Fdeath", it said.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/9
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,368,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1779109902
OL,3,CSchool issued with government funding
OL,4,Cthreat after teen's murder
OL,6,FIn a statement St Clare Catholic Multi
OL,7,FAcademy Trust said it had already
OL,8,Ftaken action to address seven points
OL,9,Fraised by the DfE.
OL,11,FA spokesperson said: "The trust has
OL,12,Fprovided information on these actions
OL,13,Fand confirmed that we will continue to
OL,14,Fwork closely with the DfE on this
OL,15,Fprocess.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G7/9
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,368,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1779109902
OL,3,CSchool issued with government funding
OL,4,Cthreat after teen's murder
OL,6,F"The board of the trust will be
OL,7,Fcollaborating with the DfE and other
OL,8,Fkey partners over the coming months to
OL,9,Ffinalise the actions and ensure that
OL,10,Fthe notice is another step in this
OL,11,Fprocess as we continuously strengthen
OL,12,Fand improve best practice. From the
OL,13,Foutset, we have proactively engaged
OL,14,Fwith the statutory safeguarding
OL,15,Fagencies and will continue to do so
OL,16,Fwith a clear focus on providing the
OL,17,Fbest possible environment for students.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G8/9
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
